clearAllRulers(25.10)                                    clearAllRulers(25.10)

Name
       clearAllRulers

Syntax
       clearAllRulers -help

       Removes  all  ruler  lines from the main window. You can also clear the
       ruler lines with the Clear All Rulers icon on the toolbar in  the  main
       window.

